<exercisegroup cols="3"><introduction><p>For Problems 1<ndash/>6, solve the system by the substitution method.
</p></introduction>

<exercise number="1"><statement><p>
    <m>\begin{aligned}[t]
        \amp y=2x\\
        \amp 3x+y=10
        \end{aligned}
    </m></p></statement>
<answer><m>(2,4)</m></answer></exercise> 

